Moatshe Ngoepe said the unknown man was wearing a light blue long sleeve
t-shirt, dark blue trouser and a blue belt with no shoes.Ngoepe said the motive behind the murder is still not clear at
this stage, but police investigations will tell as they are still unfolding.He said no arrests have been made so far, but cops are still
investigation.Ngoepe said urged anyone with information which can lead to the
arrest of the suspects involved in this murder may contact Detective Sergeant
